    "Therefore, delivering personalized Parsons puzzles as scaffolding can encourage students to cognitively attend to the practice material.",
    "This approach has the potential to provide greater learning than just reading text.",
    "This goal drove the design of CodeTailor to deliver Parsons puzzles as scaffolding to support students who struggle while programming.",
